"while different filter groups will be ANDed together. Undefined group "
"keys are treated as unique groups, i.e. are not grouped together. For "
"example, if a table has three filters, of which two are for departments "
"Finance and Marketing (group key = 'department'), and one refers to the "
"region Europe (group key = 'region'), the filter clause would apply the "
"filter (department = 'Finance' OR department = 'Marketing') AND (region ="
" 'Europe')."
msgstr "Suodattimet kanssa the sama ryhmä avain will olla ORed together within the ryhmä, kun different suodatin groups will olla ANDed together. Undefined ryhmä keys ovat treated as unique groups, i.e. ovat ei ryhmitelty together. Varten esimerkki, jos a taulu has three suodattimet, -sta joka two ovat varten departments Finance ja Marketing (ryhmä avain = 'department'), ja yksi refers to the region Europe (ryhmä avain = 'region'), the suodatin clause would käytä the suodatin (department = 'Finance' OR department = 'Marketing') AND (region = 'Europe')."

