"as an edge in the chart."
msgstr "Visualisoi a parallel aseta -sta mittarit across multiple groups. Each ryhmä on visualized käyttäen its own viiva -sta pisteet ja each mittari on represented as an edge sisään the kaavio."

msgid ""
"Visualize a related metric across pairs of groups. Heatmaps excel at "
"showcasing the correlation or strength between two groups. Color is used "
"to emphasize the strength of the link between each pair of groups."
msgstr "Visualisoi a related mittari across pairs -sta groups. Heatmaps excel kohdassa showcasing the correlation tai strength välillä two groups. Väri on käytetty to emphasize the strength -sta the link välillä each pair -sta groups."

